What is SDLC:
  It is a process used in sw industry  iwth set of statndards to design , develop and test
The actual end goal of this is to dfeliver high quality product
There are dff phases here in loop
1. Planning
2. Defining
3. Designing
4. Building(SW)
5. Testing
6. Deploy

Example of
# PLanning -- Req gathering and feedback from customer
Defining -- Preparing documents for all the research and feeback with the specifications
Designing -- low, HIgh level design
Building -- It means devoloping the code and push to GIT 
Testing -- A server will be created by QE and test the code
Deploy -- once testing is done, app will be deployed to prod and then to customer
So this will make sure quick process, automate wich leads to efficiency
